data.description: Beautifully updated historic home, move in ready, appliances included but not warranted by the sellers.  You will love the updated floors, ten-foot ceilings, gas log fireplace in the family room and large covered porch.  The kitchen is over-sized, tons of cabinet space with a built in oven and gas cooktop, stainless dishwasher and refrigerator, plenty of room to host big gatherings.  The large dining room is perfect for all your family to come together.  There is also a full bath plus laundry room, washer & dryer included, on the main floor.  All three bedrooms and another full bath upstairs make the home feel spacious.  You will love the detached two car garage with room for a workbench.  A new black chain-link fence has been installed already for you.  Seller reports new roof and gutters in 2021.  This charming home is waiting for you!  Home to be sold as is.
